Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來吹獨奏部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是中世古同學 而是由你來 你明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從大清早直至傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著暑假的到來練習時間照理變長了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但轉眼間就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家甚至都覺得還不夠的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然發生了那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那段 上低音號能一起吹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第162小節 和低音大提琴合奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃前醬 能行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美子醬 是這一段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}重音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}細心！不要走音
